<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><style>
  :root { --accent: #fbbf24; --teal: #5eead4; --pink: #fb7185; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html, body { width: 1080px; height: 1440px; overflow: hidden;
    font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
    color: #fff;
    background:
      radial-gradient(900px 700px at 50% 100%, rgba(251,191,36,0.22), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(800px 600px at 20% 30%, rgba(251,113,133,0.14), transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0f1e 0%, #07091a 100%);
  }
  .frame { position: absolute; inset: 0; padding: 80px 70px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .num { font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: 6px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }

  .center { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; gap: 30px; }
  h2 {
    font-size: 96px; line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 900;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #c2c9dc);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  h2 .emoji { -webkit-text-fill-color: initial; background: none; }
  .stab {
    font-size: 38px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-weight: 600;
  }
  .stab em { background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 60%, rgba(251,191,36,0.4) 60%);
    font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 900; padding: 0 6px; }

  .actions {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .action {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 22px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .action .icon {
    font-size: 50px; width: 70px; text-align: center;
  }
  .action .lhs { flex: 1; }
  .action .ttl { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; }
  .action .sub2 { font-size: 22px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 500; }
  .action.pri {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251,191,36,0.18), rgba(251,113,133,0.08));
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(251,191,36,0.2);
  }

  .bottom {
    text-align: center; padding-top: 30px;
    border-top: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    font-size: 28px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .bottom .heart { color: var(--pink); }
  .bottom b { color: var(--accent); }
</style></head>
<body>
<div class="frame">
  <div class="num">CTA · 05</div>

  <div class="center">
    <h2>下次 demo day<br>不用再蹲展区<span class="emoji">😎</span></h2>
    <div class="stab">
      把项目卡照片扔进 Skill<br>
      <em>30 分钟</em> 后所有项目摆面前
    </div>

    <div class="actions">
      <div class="action pri">
        <div class="icon">⭐</div>
        <div class="lhs">
          <div class="ttl">点赞收藏</div>
          <div class="sub2">下次想用直接翻回来 🔖</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="action">
        <div class="icon">💬</div>
        <div class="lhs">
          <div class="ttl">评论区聊</div>
          <div class="sub2">想用在 YC / 红杉 / 经纬路演？我帮你看下</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="action">
        <div class="icon">🔥</div>
        <div class="lhs">
          <div class="ttl">关注我</div>
          <div class="sub2">AI x 创业实操干货 每周更</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom">
    <span class="heart">❤️</span> 这是 AI 真正改变工作方式的方式<br>
    不是替你思考，是把<b>「思考前必须做的脏活」</b>全部接走
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>
